    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a refined example of automotive engineering, this vehicle offers a harmonious balance of performance and reliability. Meticulously maintained to ensure consistent operational excellence, it stands as a testament to enduring quality. Featuring a well-appointed interior and a robust drivetrain, this selection represents a sophisticated choice for the discerning driver seeking dependable luxury and proven mechanical standards.",
      "price": 34500.0,
